=== Description ===
A convenient shorthand to make an inline link to an article's discussion (Talk:) page. It shows like this{{discuss}} inline.

=== Usage ===
 <nowiki>{{</nowiki>discuss<nowiki>}}</nowiki>
 
 <nowiki>{{</nowiki>discuss|''section''<nowiki>}}</nowiki>
 <nowiki>{{</nowiki>discuss|section=''section''<nowiki>}}</nowiki>
 
 <nowiki>{{</nowiki>discuss|''section''|''text''<nowiki>}}</nowiki>
 <nowiki>{{</nowiki>discuss|section=''section''|text=''text''<nowiki>}}</nowiki>
Where:
* <kbd>''section''</kbd> is the optional section within the Talk: page (default: the top of the page).
* <kbd>''text''</kbd> is the optional alternate link text displayed (default: "''discuss''").

